igate-unprecedented-leak-of-reasonableness-standard-decision/0000018d-7ad6-d008-a9cd-fbf7b2600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列财长承诺积极反对美国对约旦河西岸定居者的制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-finance-minister-pledges-to-actively-oppose-american-sanctions-on-w-bank-settlers/0000018d-7aa0-dcdb-a58d-ffbdab380000</link><description>几位以色列议员严厉批评拜登对约旦河西岸暴力定居者的新制裁，以及开始执行这些制裁的两家以色列银行</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 20:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-finance-minister-pledges-to-actively-oppose-american-sanctions-on-w-bank-settlers/0000018d-7aa0-dcdb-a58d-ffbdab380000</guid></item><item><title>马尔万·巴尔古提 (Marwan Barghouti) 是谁？被监禁的恐怖分子还是巴勒斯坦曼德拉？为什么哈马斯希望释放他？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-is-marwan-barghouti-jailed-terrorist-or-palestinian-mandela/0000018d-794b-dd6e-a98d-fd6b6b8e0000</link><description>长期以来被视为巴勒斯坦权力机构主席马哈茂德·阿巴斯的继任者的马尔万·巴尔古提因谋杀罪在以色列服五次无期徒刑。哈马斯特别要求在可能的人质囚犯交换中释放他。巴尔古提是团结的实用主义者还是恐怖分子的策划者？</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 19:43:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/who-is-marwan-barghouti-jailed-terrorist-or-palestinian-mandela/0000018d-794b-dd6e-a98d-fd6b6b8e0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列极右翼反对释放哈马斯扣押的以色列人质的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-05/ty-article/.highlight/why-israels-far-right-opposes-a-deal-to-free-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018d-7a76-d9fb-a9fd-feff97bb0000</link><description>尽管我们过去失败了，但我们有一个完整的假设未来来阻止我们被迫释放的任何邪恶。与鲁莽的部长本·格维尔（Ben-Gvir）强迫他的保安玩捉迷藏不同，人质已经没有时间了</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 18:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-05/ty-article/.highlight/why-israels-far-right-opposes-a-deal-to-free-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018d-7a76-d9fb-a9fd-feff97bb0000</guid></item><item><title>卫星图像显示以色列对真主党无人机基地的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-strike-on-hezbollah-drone-base-revealed-in-satellite-images/0000018d-7a19-dcdb-a58d-ff1da1370000</link><description>十天前真主党向以色列铁穹电池发射攻击无人机后，黎巴嫩空军基地成为袭击目标。新的镜头显示了受损的跑道和附近的机库</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 17:46:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-strike-on-hezbollah-drone-base-revealed-in-satellite-images/0000018d-7a19-dcdb-a58d-ff1da1370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院批准对被指控妨碍谋杀调查的警察进行宽大的认罪交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-approves-plea-bargain-for-cop-charged-with-obstructing-murder-investigation/0000018d-79d4-d008-a9cd-fbf5c55a0000</link><description>首席准尉哈伊姆·加拜 (Chaim Gabai) 未能报告他与以色列北部谋杀案主要嫌疑人的关系，将被判犯有欺诈和背信罪，而对他的主要指控——妨碍司法公正——则被撤销</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 17:21:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-approves-plea-bargain-for-cop-charged-with-obstructing-murder-investigation/0000018d-79d4-d008-a9cd-fbf5c55a0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔部长逃离约旦河西岸的安全时，保镖被迫追赶他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/bodyguards-forced-to-chase-minister-ben-gvir-as-he-flees-his-own-security-in-the-west-bank/0000018d-79c6-d9fb-a9fd-ffdfca510000</link><description>拥有最严格安全级别的以色列国家安全部长对他的安全团队感到愤怒，并在警卫还没准备好后就上了邻居的车</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 17:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/bodyguards-forced-to-chase-minister-ben-gvir-as-he-flees-his-own-security-in-the-west-bank/0000018d-79c6-d9fb-a9fd-ffdfca510000</guid></item><item><title>由于需求低迷，以色列航空公司取消了夏季飞往​​都柏林和马拉喀什的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/el-al-cancels-summer-flights-to-dublin-and-marrakech-due-to-low-demand/0000018d-79d7-d008-a9cd-fbf75bd30000</link><description>以色列航空公司坚称取消两条线路的决定完全是基于客户的需求，而不是基于爱尔兰和摩洛哥对以色列加沙战争的政治立场</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:11:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/el-al-cancels-summer-flights-to-dublin-and-marrakech-due-to-low-demand/0000018d-79d7-d008-a9cd-fbf75bd30000</guid></item><item><title>第二家以色列银行根据美国制裁封锁西岸定居者的账户</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/second-israeli-bank-blocks-west-bank-settlers-account-in-compliance-with-u-s-sanctions/0000018d-795e-de30-a5dd-79ffa4990000</link><description>以色列政府拥有的邮政银行关闭了被列入美国制裁名单的戴维·柴·哈斯代 (David Chai Hasdai) 的账户，而一天前以色列银行也采取了类似行动；以色列央行发表声明支持雷米遵守制裁的决定</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:02:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/second-israeli-bank-blocks-west-bank-settlers-account-in-compliance-with-u-s-sanctions/0000018d-795e-de30-a5dd-79ffa4990000</guid></item><item><title>新星党大屠杀受害者家属要求以色列立法者给出答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/families-of-nova-party-massacre-victims-demand-answers-from-israeli-lawmakers/0000018d-7986-d008-a9cd-fbf7fbf50000</link><description>家人在议会听证会上表示，他们没有收到有关亲人遭遇的信息，国家也没有向他们提供支持</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 15:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/families-of-nova-party-massacre-victims-demand-answers-from-israeli-lawmakers/0000018d-7986-d008-a9cd-fbf7fbf50000</guid></item><item><title>14 岁巴勒斯坦少年在耶路撒冷附近企图刺伤后被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/14-year-old-palestinian-shot-and-killed-after-attempted-stabbing-near-jerusalem/0000018d-79ad-d008-a9cd-fbfd97a90000</link><description>警方称，这名名叫瓦迪·奥维萨特 (Wadee&amp;#39; Oweisat) 的青少年引起了警方的怀疑，并在警方开始搜查他后试图刺伤他们。边防警察指挥官告诉官员，“这正是我对我们战士在每场比赛中的期望”</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 15:25:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/14-year-old-palestinian-shot-and-killed-after-attempted-stabbing-near-jerusalem/0000018d-79ad-d008-a9cd-fbfd97a90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的艺术和文学也压制了加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-art-and-literature-have-repressed-gaza-too/0000018d-78c4-dd6e-a98d-fce65d040000</link><description>近几十年来，以色列社会与加沙的关系日益疏远，导致其在文化上基本上被忽视，确实涉及这一问题的作品承认，只能通过军事过滤器才能看到它</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 14:02:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-art-and-literature-have-repressed-gaza-too/0000018d-78c4-dd6e-a98d-fce65d040000</guid></item><item><title>海法市试图阻止出版一本有关以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-seeks-to-block-launch-of-a-book-on-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018d-78c8-d971-a38f-79fab7e30000</link><description>居民们对即将举行的活动表示反对，该活动计划推出该书的希伯来语译本，该书讲述了两个失去亲人的父亲（一个是以色列人，另一个是巴勒斯坦人）之间的友谊故事。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-seeks-to-block-launch-of-a-book-on-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018d-78c8-d971-a38f-79fab7e30000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔国家基金的以色列律师在人质谈判中为军队提供建议；以色列国防军：“不存在利益冲突”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lawyer-to-qatari-state-fund-advises-idf-in-hostage-negotiations/0000018d-7929-d4f1-a18d-fd7954b70000</link><description>律师约瑟夫·本克尔代表卡塔尔慈善机构，这是卡塔尔政府控制的一个基金会，曾被用来向哈马斯转移资金。战争爆发后，本克尔被征召入以色列陆军预备役，担任人质谈判顾问</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:20:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lawyer-to-qatari-state-fund-advises-idf-in-hostage-negotiations/0000018d-7929-d4f1-a18d-fd7954b70000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙，一名六岁儿童躺在坦克前的尸体中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/in-gaza-a-6-year-old-lies-before-a-tank-among-the-bodies/0000018d-78b1-d4f1-a18d-fcf145400000</link><description>Hind Hamada 这个名字对以色列人来说没有任何意义。为什么会这样呢？但她的笑脸现在可能已为每个巴勒斯坦家庭所熟悉。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/in-gaza-a-6-year-old-lies-before-a-tank-among-the-bodies/0000018d-78b1-d4f1-a18d-fcf145400000</guid></item><item><title>美国是否终于揭穿了伊朗的虚张声势，对德黑兰支持的民兵进行了打击？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/is-the-u-s-finally-calling-irans-bluff-with-strikes-on-tehran-backed-militias/0000018d-78b1-dd6e-a98d-fcb3910c0000</link><description>美国最近对叙利亚、伊拉克和也门民兵组织的袭击没有具体的战略目标，也无意实现任何超出其目标的目标，但它们仍然可以重新洗牌伊朗认为自己完全控制的地区格局</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/is-the-u-s-finally-calling-irans-bluff-with-strikes-on-tehran-backed-militias/0000018d-78b1-dd6e-a98d-fcb3910c0000</guid></item><item><title>在主要捐助者因以色列指控而暂停援助后，西班牙将向近东救济工程处额外提供 380 万美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/spain-to-give-unrwa-extra-3-8-million-after-donors-suspend-aid-amid-israeli-allegations/0000018d-794d-d008-a9cd-fbfda3ce0000</link><description>邻国葡萄牙宣布向近东救济工程处提供价值100万欧元的额外援助。其外交部长写道，“在这个困难时刻，不要背弃巴勒斯坦人民”，这一点至关重要</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:01:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/spain-to-give-unrwa-extra-3-8-million-after-donors-suspend-aid-amid-israeli-allegations/0000018d-794d-d008-a9cd-fbfda3ce0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争打造了一部混乱的混搭音乐剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/the-war-in-gaza-has-created-a-chaotic-mash-up-musical/0000018d-74b8-d4f1-a18d-f4f8d56e0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，任何人都在发行歌曲，但一位从未录制过歌曲的艺术家伊丹·阿梅迪 (Idan Amedi) 成为了新闻头条。此外，一部有关六日战争的新音乐剧登陆以色列银幕</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 10:12:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/the-war-in-gaza-has-created-a-chaotic-mash-up-musical/0000018d-74b8-d4f1-a18d-f4f8d56e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>